text: Marlene Kahler (born 15 May 2001) is an Austrian swimmer. She competed in the women's 200 metre freestyle at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Austrian female freestyle swimmers
